    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2133757239" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15995905290142829963">Such a fascinating and gut wrenching account of a storm that affected so many lives. An odd half documentary/half story-telling feel to it and as it doesn’t try to fictionalize anything allows the reader to come to her own conclusion about the final moments of the Andrea Gail. It starts out strong, gets a bit too technical in the middle, but finishes as a page turner with true accounts from others who survived the storm. All in all, a really great book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


